    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver, though it shows clear signs of its age and use. The exterior has several noticeable scratches, small door dings, and some fading in the clear coat on the hood. Inside, the upholstery has some staining and a small tear on the driver's side bolster, and the dashboard has a minor crack. Mechanically, the car starts and runs, but it will likely need new tires and a brake service in the near future. It\u2019s an honest, functional car for someone looking for affordable transportation who doesn't mind some cosmetic imperfections.",
