      "description": "Hey there! I'm selling my awesome ride that\u2019s been such a reliable companion for me. It\u2019s in great shape and totally ready for its next big adventure! It runs super smooth and has been very well-cared for over the years. If you\u2019re looking for a dependable car that still looks and feels fantastic, you\u2019re going to love this one. Come take it for a spin and see for yourself!",
      "price": 32000.0,
