    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a meticulously maintained silver metallic SUV that strikes the perfect balance between luxury and utility. The exterior retains a deep, lustrous shine; while there are a few minor stone chips on the front fascia and a small scuff on the rear bumper consistent with daily use, the body remains straight and free of major dents. Inside, the charcoal leather upholstery is supple and free of tears, showing only light bolster wear on the driver's side. All cabin amenities, including the dual-zone climate control, heated seats, and the premium 10-speaker sound system, are in full working order. Mechanically, this vehicle is sound, featuring a comprehensive service log with oil changes performed every 5,000 miles. The engine idles quietly, and the transmission shifts seamlessly through all gears. Recent maintenance includes a fresh set of all-season tires with over 80% tread life remaining and a cooling system flush. This is a smoke-free, pet-free vehicle that has been primarily garage-kept, offering a reliable and polished driving experience for its next owner.",
